          content:
            '<h2><strong>Introduction - What Is Altseason?</strong></h2><p>“Altseason” refers to a period when alternative cryptocurrencies (altcoins) outperform the market leader, Bitcoin (BTC). In simple terms, it’s when investors shift capital from Bitcoin into other tokens. According to the <a href="https://www.blockchaincenter.net/en/altcoin-season-index/">Altcoin Season Index</a>, recent readings have climbed into the 70s out of 100 - the highest levels in 2025 so far. This blog explains why smaller tokens are gaining momentum now, what sectors are leading the move, and how investors can approach this opportunity with clear strategy.</p>',
