          content: `<h2><strong>The Verdict</strong></h2><p>There's no universal "winner" - it depends on your situation.</p><p><strong>Republic</strong> is a solid choice for accredited investors who want a proven platform with diverse deal types and don't mind illiquidity.</p><p><strong>IPO Genie</strong> is built for investors who want:</p><ul><li>AI-powered curation reducing research burden</li><li>Token-based access without high minimums</li><li>Focus on pre-IPO opportunities specifically</li><li>Liquidity through tradeable tokens</li><li>Participation in platform economics</li></ul><p>The best approach? Understand both, use what fits your strategy. Many savvy investors allocate across platforms to capture deal variety from Republic and AI-curated pre-IPO focus from IPO Genie.</p><figure><a href="https://buy.ipogenie.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/images/blog/ai-scoring-model/presale-cta.webp" alt="IPO Genie Presale" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><p><strong>Related:</strong> <a href="/learn/pre-ipo-investing">What is Pre-IPO Investing?</a> | <a href="/how-it-works">How IPO Genie Works</a></p>`,
